<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Mon, 29 Jun 2026 15:26:03 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>Strategy表示可能会出售高达12.5亿美元的比特币</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-29/strategy-says-it-may-sell-up-to-1-25-billlion-of-bitcoin</link><description>Michael Saylor 的 Strategy Inc. 公布了对其比特币战略基础的融资模式的彻底改革，赋予自己更广泛的权力来出售加密货币、回购证券和保持流动性，以适应多年来积极积累的结构所承受的越来越大的压力。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ifEH6z6pWrqE/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jun 2026 12:19:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-29/strategy-says-it-may-sell-up-to-1-25-billlion-of-bitcoin</guid></item><item><title>比特币 ETF 遭遇 40 亿美元资金流出最糟糕月份</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-29/bitcoin-btc-etfs-face-record-4-billion-in-june-outflows-worst-since-launch</link><description>在美国上市的比特币交易所交易基金正面临自两年前推出以来最糟糕的一个月提款情况。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ipx2T93hKbqU/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jun 2026 08:24:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-29/bitcoin-btc-etfs-face-record-4-billion-in-june-outflows-worst-since-launch</guid></item><item><title>日本预测市场初创公司利用忠诚度积分绕过赌博禁令</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-29/prediction-markets-emerge-in-japan-with-shopping-vouchers</link><description>&lt;p&gt;被禁止进行真钱赌博的本土平台正在利用该国的忠诚积分文化来打造 Polymarket 的替代品。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iiFokDqmuELQ/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 29 Jun 2026 02:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/